<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFWray.2C_Andrew">Wray, Andrew (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2002-11-11"><a href="/wiki/2002" title="2002">2002</a>-<a href="/wiki/November_11" title="November 11">11-11</a></span>). <a href="http://listserv.nd.edu/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind0211&amp;L=pamnet&amp;T=0&amp;F=&amp;S=&amp;P=3647" class="external text" title="http://listserv.nd.edu/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind0211&amp;L=pamnet&amp;T=0&amp;F=&amp;S=&amp;P=3647" rel="nofollow">"Classical and Quantum Gravity"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://listserv.nd.edu/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind0211&amp;L=pamnet&amp;T=0&amp;F=&amp;S=&amp;P=3647" class="external free" title="http://listserv.nd.edu/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind0211&amp;L=pamnet&amp;T=0&amp;F=&amp;S=&amp;P=3647" rel="nofollow">http://listserv.nd.edu/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind0211&amp;L=pamnet&amp;T=0&amp;F=&amp;S=&amp;P=3647</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-12-12</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Classical+and+Quantum+Gravity&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Wray%2C+Andrew&amp;rft.au=Wray%2C+Andrew&amp;rft.date=%5B%5B2002-11-11%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Flistserv.nd.edu%2Fcgi-bin%2Fwa%3FA2%3Dind0211%26L%3Dpamnet%26T%3D0%26F%3D%26S%3D%26P%3D3647&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bogdanov_Affair"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
